text: Kiel () is a city in the north of Germany. It is the capital of the state of Schleswig-Holstein. It has a population of 239,526 people."population of Schleswig-Holstein (German)"http://www.statistik- nord.de/uploads/tx_standocuments/A_I_2_vj104_S.pdf It is a port on the sea and has an oceanic climate (Cfb in the Koeppen climate classification). ==References== ==Other websites== Category:Port cities and towns of the Baltic Sea Category:Ports and harbours of Germany
